****** OTHER SOFTWARE

For one of our examples, we use the Degrafa library which is also licensed under the MIT license.  You can
read more about that here: http://degrafa.org/

We include the Degrafa library in our libs folder to make building the example easier. You don't not need to
include this in your project unless you plan on using Degrafa as well.


 
